💻 Code Hub
🧑‍💻 Developed by Gopi Krishna
📝 Description

Code Hub is a front-end web project built using HTML and CSS.
It serves as a learning platform where users can explore programming domains like Frontend, Backend, AI, DSA, and Cybersecurity.
The page includes a sign-in form, coding categories, assignment sections, and progress indicators.

🚀 Features

Organized sections for different coding fields

Circular progress bars showing learning progress

Beginner, Intermediate, and Advanced assignment boxes

Interactive sign-in form

Gradient background with hover effects

🛠️ Technologies

HTML5

CSS3 (Flexbox, Gradients, Hover effects)
